vrpRep.structure.instance

Class Instance

  • java.lang.Object
    • vrpRep.structure.instance.Instance

  • public class Instance
extends java.lang.Object
    Main class of default instance structure.
    Class should be used access Request, Link, Node, Vehicle and Network information. All elements are accessed statically. i.e. Instance.XXX where XXX is either a variable or method name
    Author:
    Maxim HOSKINS, Romain LIENARD, Raphael MOLY and Alexandre RENAUD
    See Also:
    Request, Link, Node, Vehicle, Network
